WiFi & BT Module
----------------

|Product| is equipped with the popular **Realtek RTL8723 WiFi/BT module** that supports BT/BLE 4.0 (with backward compatibility), as well as 802.11bgn 2.4 GHz Wireless LAN (WLAN). 

.. figure:: /Media/ARM/A8/AM3354/WiFi_BT.jpeg
   :align: center
   :figclass: align-center

   *Figure 12a: RTL8273 WiFi/BT Module*

The enclosed (PPC) variant of the product also includes an SMA connector for an external WiFi/BT antenna, as illustrated in the figure below.

.. figure:: /Media/ARM/A8/AM3354/Antenna.jpeg
   :align: center
   :figclass: align-center

   *RTL8273 WiFi/BT Module*


.. note::

    #) The product does not come shipped with the WiFi/BT module by default.
    #) If the operator mounts the WiFi/BT module on the |product| industrial PC, the module uses the USB1 channel to communicate with CPU, so it will occupy the USB1 channel.

